# Security & Protected Areas
- **NEVER** modify or read: `.env`, `.env.*`, `config/secrets.*`, `*.pem`, `*.key`.
- **Auth Modules** are Read-Only (ask before refactoring):
  - `components/global/WithAuth.tsx`
  - `src/utils/api/authInterceptor.ts`
  - `src/utils/api/axios.ts`
- **CI/CD**: Never modify `.github/workflows/**`.
- **Package Manager**: Treat `yarn.lock` as read-only unless adding dependencies.
